            <title>[LOG4J2-1103] Failover appender does not fail over</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1103</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We are using the attached configuration (which follows the manual) that defines one failover appender. But this is not used and log4j complains&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;ERROR appender Failover has no parameter that matches element Failovers&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
